                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I venture to predict the articles you might occasionally<lb/>\n                                        insert in the occident elucidating the points in\n                                        question<lb/> would not be considered the least interesting\n                                        in it.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Will you thank <persName>Mr. Sibreuce</persName>\n                                        for the message<lb/> conveyed to me through you &amp;\n                                        believe me</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Revd Sir Yours sincerely</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A A. Lindo</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <div>\n                                        <p>\n                                                  <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_6_9.pdf\">The above\n                                                  text refers to Occident Volume 6 No. 9 pages 421\n                                                  through 436. Click here to view.</ref>\n                                        </p>\n                              </div>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
